    {
      "text": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\tSussing Out \u2014 and Stopping \u2014 Illegal Dumping\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tPhilly has more illegal dumping surveillance cameras than other major cities, but far fewer arrests and convictions. Here\u2019s what we know about illegal dumpers \u2014 and a system that rarely stops them.\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tBy Nick Russo\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t",
