      "text": "\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tWatch: Citizen Book Club with Dan Pfeiffer\t\tThe author, podcaster and political insider spoke to a Philadelphia Citizen audience about uniting America by telling the truth.\n\t\t\tBy Lauren McCutcheon\t\n\t",
